title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC.description: Allows an app to use device supported biometric modalities.

android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT.description: This constant was deprecated in API level 28. Applications should request USE_BIOMETRIC instead

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

manifest_analysis.title:
Service (com.crypter.cryptocyrrency.notifications.MyFirebaseMessagingService) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

"about_Crypterium_Gas_text" : "CRPT tokens are used as “fuel” for performing crypto-fiat transactions with Crypterium app. You can compare it to “gas” powering the transactions on Ethereum.
Everytime someone makes a payment using Crypterium app, a fee equal to 0.5% of the value of the transaction in CRPT is taken from user’s account and burned as fuel.
For example, if you buy a cup of coffee for $3, you'll pay the equivalent of $3 in chosen cryptocurrency, and the commission of $0.015 (0.5%) in CRPT at their current rate.
The "burning process" of CRPT is regulated by the smart-contract, and conducted at the current exchange rate. This means the number of CRPT tokens will be reducing over time."

"crpt_about" : "Assim como uma máquina necessita de combustível para operar, as soluções de pagamento da Crypterium funcionam à base de tokens CRPT. Toda vez que alguém fizer um pagamento, uma taxa equivalente a 0,5% do valor da transação é retirado da conta do usuário e "queimada". Isso significa que o número de tokens CRPT reduzirá com o passar do tempo. 

Tokens CRPT também podem ser usados como forma de pagar taxas ligadas a outras transações (que não as cripto-dinheiro) no app Crypterium – por um período limitado ou indefinidamente, a critério exclusivo da Crypterium. Nesse caso, os tokens CRPT podem ser usados como forma de pagamento única, ou como forma de pagar as taxas de transação. Diferentemente de tokens usados para pagar taxas ligadas a pagamentos cripto-dinheiro, os tokens CRPT podem não ser queimados. 

Durante a venda de tokens, a Crypterium emitiu 99,983,677 tokens antes de atingir o limite estabelecido pelo governo britânico no White Paper. Como especificado, 70% dessa quantia foi para aqueles que compraram tokens durante a Oferta Inicial de Moedas, e os 30% restantes foram reservados para necessidades futuras do projeto. "cryptoToFiatGasDescription" : "Los tokens CRPT se utilizan como "combustible" para realizar transacciones cripto-fiat en la aplicación Crypterium. Puede compararlo con el "gas" que alimenta las transacciones en Ethereum.

Cada vez que alguien realiza un pago con la aplicación Crypterium, se deduce una comisión equivalente al 0,5% del valor de la transacción en CRPT y se consume como combustible.

Por ejemplo, si compra un café por $3, pagará el equivalente a $3 en su criptomoneda seleccionada, y la comisión de $0.015 (0.5%) en CRPT a su tasa actual.

"crpt_about" : "Так же, как машина работает на топливе, платежные операции Crypterium поддерживаются токенами CRPT. Каждый раз, когда кто-то совершает платеж, со счета пользователя взимается комиссия, равная 0,5% от стоимости сделки в CRPT. Это означает, что число токенов CRPT будет со временем сокращаться. CRPT токены также могут использоваться в качестве метода оплаты сборов, применяемых к другим, не криптографическим, транзакциям в приложении Crypterium - в течение ограниченного периода времени или неограниченно, по усмотрению компании Crypterium. В этом случае токены CRPT могут использоваться как единственное или дополнительное средство оплаты комиссионных за транзакции. В отличие от токенов, используемых для оплаты сборов, применяемых к криптографическим платежам, эти токены CRPT не могут быть сожжены. В ходе продажи токенов Crypterium выпустил 99 983 677 токенов. 70% этой суммы было отправлено тем, кто купил токены во время ICO, а остальные 30% были зарезервированы для нужд проекта. Больше токенов выпущено не будет. Токены CRPT, принадлежащие членам команды, блокируются на 10 месяцев с момента окончания продажи токенов."

"crpt_about" : "Al igual que una máquina funciona con combustible, las soluciones de pago de Crypterium están impulsadas por tokens CRPT. Cada vez que alguien realiza un pago, se toma de la cuenta del usuario y se consume una tarifa equivalente al 0,5% del valor de la transacción en CRPT. Esto significa que la cantidad de tokens de CRPT se reducirá con el tiempo.

Las CRPT también se pueden usar como un método para pagar tarifas aplicadas a otras transacciones que sean crypto, en la aplicación Crypterium, por un período de tiempo limitado o por tiempo indefinido, a discreción exclusiva de Crypterium. En este caso, los tokens CRPT se pueden utilizar como un medio único o adicional para pagar las tarifas de transacción. A diferencia de los tokens que se utilizan para pagar los aranceles que se aplican a los pagos crypto-fiat, esos tokens CRPT no se pueden quemar.

Durante la venta del token, Crypterium emitió 99,983,677 tokens antes de llegar al límite designado en la Documentación Técnica. Como se especificó, el 70% de esta cantidad se destinó a quienes compraron fichas durante el ICO, y el otro 30%se reservó para las necesidades del proyecto. No se añadirán más tokens. Las fichas CRPT que pertenecen a los miembros del equipo están bloqueadas por un período de 10 meses desde el final de la venta de la ficha."

Crypterium loyalty program applies to crypto-to-fiat payments to merchants and does not cover all transactions preformed in the Crypterium service.

Crypterium shall retain the right to change terms and conditions of unsecured loyalty program.

"cryptoToFiatGasDescription" : "Os tokens CRPT são usados como “combustível” para realizar transações cripto-para-dinheiro pelo app da Crypterium. Você pode comparar isso com o ETH sendo o combustível para as transações da Ethereum. 

 Toda vez que alguém fizer um pagamento usando o app da Crypterium, uma taxa de 0,5% do valor da transação em CRPT será debitada da conta do usuário e queimada como combustível. 

Por exemplo, se você comprar um café por R$3,00, você pagará o equivalente a R$3,00 com a criptomoeda selecionada, mais a taxa de comissão de R$0,015 (0,5%) em CRPT de acordo com o câmbio do momento. 

O "processo de queima" do CRPT é regulado por contratos inteligentes, e é conduzido de acordo com a taxa de câmbio do momento. Isso significa que o número de tokens CRPT reduzirá com o passar do tempo."

"loyalty_description_second" : "O token-de-volta do usuário Crypterium será distribuído por meio de um fundo de lealdade mensal (FLM). Uma parte específica (baseada na margem da Crypterium por um vendedor específico) de todo pagamento cripto-para-dinheiro feito por meio da Crypterium será alocado para o fundo geral de fidelidade, na moeda do pagamento feito. Depois, a Crypterium irá abertamente adquirir tokens CRPT disponíveis no mercado secundário para os fundos gerados durante o mês.

Estes são os nossos gastos com marketing para divulgar e incentivar as atividades financeiras do usuário. Em seguida, o FML será dividido em 4 partes, baseando-se em 4 grupos de usuários: (Bronze – 5%, Silver – 10%, Gold – 35%, Platinum – 50%). Por fim, os tokens serão transferidos para a conta do usuário Crypterium, respeitando a proporção do seu referido grupo de usuário.

Essa proporção será medida da seguinte forma: proporção entre todos os pagamentos cripto-para-dinheiro feitos por um usuário específico durante um determinado mês, com o total de pagamentos cripto-para-dinheiro feitos pelo grupo de usuários durante um determinado mês.

O programa de fidelidade da Crypterium refere-se a pagamentos de natureza cripto-para-dinheiro efetuados, e não abrange todas as transações realizadas dentro da Crypterium.

A Crypterium reserva-se o direito de alterar os termos e condições de seu programa de fidelidade.

O programa de fidelidade será lançado durante o primeiro trimestre de 2019. Antes do lançamento do programa, a taxa de comissão do projeto (pago pelos comerciantes para transações cripto-para-dinheiro) tem poucas chances de ser significativa. Dessa forma, o fundo de fidelidade não terá lucros."

"cryptoToFiatGasDescription" : "CRPT tokens are used as “fuel” for performing crypto-fiat transactions with Crypterium app. You can compare it to “gas” powering the transactions on Ethereum.

Every time someone makes a payment using Crypterium app, a fee equal to 0.5% of the value of the transaction in CRPT is taken from user’s account and burned as fuel.

For example, if you buy a cup of coffee for $3, you'll pay the equivalent of $3 in chosen cryptocurrency, and the commission of $0.015 (0.5%) in CRPT at their current rate.

The “burning process” of CRPT is regulated by the smart-contract, and conducted at the current exchange rate. This means the number of CRPT tokens will be reducing over time."

"loyalty_description_second" : "Кэшбек Crypterium будет распространяться через независимый ежемесячный фонд лояльности (MLF). Определенная часть (на основе маржи Crypterium, генерируемой конкретным продавцом) каждого крипто-фиатного платежа, произведенного через Crypterium в валюте платежа, должна быть выделена в общий фонд лояльности. Затем Crypterium будет открыто приобретать токены CRPT, доступные на вторичном рынке, за средства, сгенерированные в течение месяца.

Это наши маркетинговые расходы по продвижению и улучшению платежной активности пользователей. Затем MLF будет разделен на 4 части на основе 4 групп пользователей (Бронзовый уровень - 5%, Серебряный уровень - 10%, Золотой уровень - 35%, Платиновый уровень - 50%). Наконец, токены будут переведены на учетную запись пользователя Crypterium пропорционально фонду его / ее группы пользователей.

Эта пропорция будет измеряться следующим образом: доля всех крипто-фиатных платежей, произведенных конкретным пользователем в течение определенного месяца, от суммы крипто-фиатных платежей, созданных всей группой пользователей за определенный месяц.

Программа лояльности Crypterium применяется к крипто-фиатным оплатам покупок и не распространяется на все транзакции, совершенные в сервисе Crypterium.

Crypterium сохраняет за собой право вносить изменения в условия программы лояльности.

Программа лояльности будет запущена в 1 квартале 2019 года. Перед запуском программы комиссия проекта (выплачиваемая торговцами за крипто-фиатные транзакции) вряд ли будет значительной. Поэтому у фонда лояльности не будет выручки."

"loyalty_description_second" : "Tokenback para usuarios Crypterium se distribuirá a través de un fondo de fidelización mensual independiente(MLF). Una parte específica (basada en el margen de Crypterium generado por un comerciante específico) de cada pago de crypto-a-fíat realizado a través de Crypterium en la moneda de pago se asignará al fondo general de lealtad. Entonces Crypterium adquirirá abiertamente tokens de CRPT disponibles en el mercado secundario para los fondos generados durante el mes.

Estos son nuestros gastos de marketing para promover y mejorar la actividad de pago del usuario. Posteriormente, MLF se dividirá en 4 partes según 4 grupos de usuarios (Bronce - 5%, Plata - 10%, Oro - 35%, Platino - 50%). Finalmente, los tokens se transferirán a la cuenta de usuario de Crypterium en proporción a su fondo de grupo de usuarios.

Esta proporción se medirá de la siguiente manera: la proporción de todos los pagos de crypto-a-fiat realizados por un usuario específico dentro de un mes específico de la cantidad del pago de crypto a fiat generado por todo el grupo de usuarios para un mes en particular.

El programa de lealtad de Crypterium se aplica a los pagos de crypto a fiat a comerciantes y no cubre todas las transacciones realizadas en el servicio de Crypterium.

Crypterium se reservará el derecho de cambiar los términos y condiciones del programa de lealtad no asegurado.

El programa de lealtad se lanzará en el primer trimestre de 2019. Antes del lanzamiento del programa, es poco probable que la comisión del proyecto (pagadera por los comerciantes por transacciones de cripto a fiat) sea significativa. Por lo tanto, el fondo de lealtad no tendrá ganancias."

"cryptoToFiatGasDescription" : "Токены CRPT используются в качестве «топлива» для выполнения криптографических транзакций в приложении Crypterium. Каждый раз, когда кто-то делает платеж с помощью приложения Crypterium, комиссия, равная 0,5% от стоимости транзакции в CRPT, берется со счета пользователя и сжигается как топливо. Например, если вы купите чашку кофе за 3 доллара США, вы заплатите эквивалент 3 долларов США в выбранной криптовалюте и комиссию в размере 0,015 доллара США (0,5%) в CRPT по текущему курсу. «Процесс сжигания» CRPT регулируется смарт-контрактом и ведется по текущему обменному курсу. playstore_details.title: Crypto App - Widgets, Alerts, News, Bitcoin Prices
playstore_details.description:
Keep track of all crypto coins in one app! Live crypto price alerts, price tracking, crypto coin news updates, live crypto conversion, crypto wallet - And so much more in the best crypto app!

Did you invest in cryptocurrencies? You want to buy and sell Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH) and other cryptocurrencies? Want to track Bitcoin rates or compare and convert Bitcoin rates against other cryptocurrencies or other currencies?

Start using the most unique and accurate Bitcoin and altcoin rate tracking, crypto news and Bitcoin rate converter app, The Crypto App, to get realtime price alerts and reminders for any cryptocurrency like for example Bitcoin, Ethereum or altcoin prices. ""The Crypto App - Widgets, Alerts, News, Bitcoin Prices"" is the best app to track Bitcoin and altcoin rates.

📈TRACK CRYPTO PRICES
If you follow crypto currencies, you will love using this Bitcoin tracker app to track real-time Bitcoin and altcoin rates. In many different ways ""The Crypto App - Ethereum Widgets, Alerts, News, Prices"" is the best app to track Bitcoin alerts, altcoin rates, LTC, Ethereum alerts or any other crypto coin – the most important part for crypto exchange. Follow any crypto from the global crypto coins list!

🔔GET CRYPTO ALERTS
Want to get crypto alerts live? You can easily track the prices of Bitcoins and 1000 other crypto currencies. Whether you want to track Bitcoin rates against ether price or Bitcoin price against ripple price, this crypto price tracking app will be extremely easy. Most unique multi-currency Bitcoin rate tracker app for Bitcoin investors.

📰FOLLOW CRYPTONEWS
Following crypto news has never been easy. We also have an embedded Twitter widget that displays any crypto coin news related. Don’t miss any valuable info that may lead to a mistake or to a missed opportunity. The most versatile crypto news update & crypto coins news app!

➡️CONVERT CRYPTO CURRENCY
Make use of our powerful crypto converter. Convert any crypto into other crypto or real currencies. We use live crypto prices when converting!

📉CRYPTO MARKET CAP
Knowing the coin market cap is always interesting and useful. Simply visit the frequently updated coinmarketcap data for any crypto currency in our separate crypto market cap section.

⭐CRYPTO WALLET
It enables you crypto exchange with the possibility to receive, send, buy and sell crypto. Crypto wallet is the protocol that generates your public and private keys, and it is connected directly to the blockchain. When you buy BTC, it will be stored in a BTC wallet, and when you buy ETH, it will be stored in an ETH wallet (and so on).

❤️WHY YOU’LL LOVE THE CRYPTO APP
The Crypto App is the most unique among all Bitcoin and crypto price tracking apps. Here are the features that make this Bitcoin price tracker app unique:

✅ Integrated with 300+ exchanges
✅ Search and filter through more than 1000+ altcoins
✅ Set priority coin list to define your favorite assets
✅ Detailed view of current cryptocurrency with chart
✅ Set price alerts
✅ Add widgets
✅ Crypto wallet - Trade, receive, send, buy and sell crypto such as Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH)...
✅ Convert between cryptocurrencies and currencies
✅ Supports USD, BTC, EUR and other currencies
✅ Stay updated with all cryptocurrency news

Don’t search for separate crypto tracking apps for each crypto coin part of the global cryptocurrency list. Now you have The Crypto App!

The Crypto App, Bitcoin price tracker app, is available for free and is dedicated to all crypto lovers.

➡️➡️➡️ Download now to get started! Track, trade, receive and send, buy and sell with #1 crypto tool worldwide!
